SnpModelConverter.h File Reference

Class collecting utility methods for reading various formats of snp models like:

  • Brlmm-p (aka labelz) used for snp5, snp6 and Axiom
  • Birdseed priors used for snp 6
  • Birdseed posteriors from snp 6.

Detailed Description

Class collecting utility methods for reading various formats of snp models like:

  • Brlmm-p (aka labelz) used for snp5, snp6 and Axiom
  • Birdseed priors used for snp 6
  • Birdseed posteriors from snp 6.
